728307f-a.title: Richmond: Amboy Road - Foster Road
728307f-a.text:
5741 Amboy Road, east of the N.E. corner of Foster Road,
showing the Starin house. The 1874 map by Beers indicates it to
have been the T. Asson residence.
1924.
P. i. Sperr.
